Small prosthetic application
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here's a little video of how I applied the prosthetic cut from my last post. 

I used @kryolanofficial Pros aide to glue it down, then I used acetone to melt the edges of the prosthetic. I proceeded to paint with @skinillustratorofficial Complexion palette and added @maekupforfilmandtv Dry blood & @maqpro artificial blood. 

I hope you enjoy!
